  <mainDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
    To tailor the SW safety lifecycle based upon the SW development phase reference model to ensure that all activities&#xD;
    and&amp;nbsp;tasks are consistent with one another. The process shall be performed according to ISO 26262 volume 2, clause&#xD;
    5.4.5.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Tailoring also takes into account any adaption of the process caused by employing configurable software.&#xD;
&lt;/p></mainDescription>
  <purpose>To tailor the SW lifecycle so that it takes into account the type of SW being developed and the reuse of qualified SW&#xD;
components or configurations.</purpose>
</org.eclipse.epf.uma:TaskDescription>
